{"tid":1790539,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"PUMA 瞄準玩家市場今日在國外推出電競專用鞋款「Active Gaming Footwear」","createTime":"2019-12-20T05:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T05:37:16.000Z","uid":3747,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fa59a4fb1b66fe0343d95621790f4746038a6215","tid":1790539,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"　　知名運動品牌 PUMA  今日在英國與澳洲推出電競專用鞋款「Active Gaming Footwear」，主要為了電競比賽活動與室內場地而設計，PUMA 強調穿起來具備無縫的舒適感受、支撐性與抓地力，讓玩家或選手可以適應不同的遊戲模式，以發揮出個人表現。<br />\n<br />\n　　PUMA 表示，此款「Active Gaming Footwear」採用加工過的針織鞋面帶來透氣性與舒適性，底部兼具韌性與柔軟度，而 TPU 材質則提供鞋子額外的支撐。<br />\n <br />\n　　雖然 PUMA 沒有明白指出「Active Gaming Footwear」 將如何幫助玩家在遊戲上的表現，但外界推測或許在遊玩 AR 或是 VR 遊戲時會有所幫助。<br />\n <br />\n　　「Active Gaming Footwear」已經在英國與澳洲上市，建議售價 80 歐元（約新台幣 2750 元）。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TFXoTc3dvco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTFXoTc3dvco&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5bc0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=5a10a646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TFXoTc3dvco</a>"},{"pid":"c364479a28a4cf649f19b5f10610bdd9aa11874b","tid":1790539,"uid":103325,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"電競？唔係坐響度打嘅咩？"},{"pid":"606c158c84f888a5fd0cba2eb62d80c9233198fa","tid":1790539,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"電競跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be829392b0c4874f88c4918cd4655ba490421b1","tid":1790539,"uid":237143,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"溝埋RGB丫笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜柒都電競"},{"pid":"20753b345a0c7384b8a139426308d0abab4bfa0d","tid":1790539,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"2be829392b0c4